title: William Bush IV
text: William G. Bush IV (born February 1968) is an American politician. He is a <a href="Democratic%20Party%20%28United%20States%29">Democratic</a> member of the <a href="Delaware%20House%20of%20Representatives">Delaware House of Representatives</a>, representing District 29. Bush was elected in the general election on November 6, 2018, winning 58 percent of the vote over <a href="United%20States%20Republican%20Party">Republican</a> candidate Robin Hayes.
